{"tid":1909722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「突發」原來高官聶德權都係手足！","createTime":"2020-03-04T07:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T00:43:23.000Z","uid":114360,"like":357,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"b047b9591f342546fc67aff1406e719ea19e6b55","tid":1909722,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】專家料首批包機最多25人湖北返港後確診<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惟隨行官員毋須檢疫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n港府今（4日）派首2架包機，接載首批在湖北的200多名港人返港隔離，當中有11位原獲接載的港人拒絕乘坐。惟外界更關注隨行官員由「疫區」返港後，毋須如平民般檢疫，不少與其共事的公務員均擔心官員有播毒風險。有份到當地的政制及內地事務局局長聶德權在出發前見記者，聲稱徵詢過4名公共衞生專家意見，並評估風險，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有高員回港後只需醫學監測，不需檢疫。</span></strong>港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良指，按當地感染人口比例，估計首批530名回港人士中，約有5至25人返港後會被驗出確診感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n多謝手足，唔該快小小同林鄭佢哋開會，唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource：【武漢肺炎】專家料首批包機最多25人湖北返港後確診 惟隨行官員毋須檢疫 <a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/wars/article/1_60670052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fwars%2Farticle%2F1_60670052&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=077f7a97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fwars%2Farticle%2F1_60670052&h=ccaed532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/wars/article/1_60670052</a>"},{"pid":"37c8508ceccbd8774f770df90ce0e4f339113e73","tid":1909722,"uid":114360,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"手足們有冇唸過去狗屋報失？"},{"pid":"54f7c123fd61e8129937fb216ceb7d4c4a83f71d","tid":1909722,"uid":8014,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"我要攬炒 地下黨成員"},{"pid":"532d4e2773b97cdad567d9e39dbdb8b2542e10d3","tid":1909722,"uid":114360,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"54f7c123fd61e8129937fb216ceb7d4c4a83f71d","tid":1909722,"uid":8014,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"